ent awaits!\n\nSincerely,\nThe BOSS", "short_description": "Hello! Welcome to TUBE Industries: a hamster owned and operated tube puzzle emporium! \n\nPrepare for a tube-based, puzzle-filled, HAM-PACKED adventure with our charismatic leader: The BOSS. Here at TUBE Industries we provide the puzzles and you provide\u2026 the brains. No shady business here!\n\nSincerely,\nThe BOSS"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://bluemonttechnology.com/game%20privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Bluemont Technology & Research, Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://tubebecontinued.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "3771364559549515"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}, {"id": "377978390272490"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["PUZZLE", "CASUAL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "533221968811847"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "404314041793201"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "404314041793201"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1669842000, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "404314041793201"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "6801010953323039", "version": "3.0.0"}, "id": "835827817436396", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename":